  "body": "\r\n\r\n## Issue\r\n\r\nWhat the issue is, in broad strokes.\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n- truffle unbox metacoin\r\n- Edit truffle.js:\r\n```\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  networks: {\r\n    development: {\r\n      host: \"127.0.0.1\",\r\n      port: 7545,\r\n      network_id: \"*\", // Match any network id\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n};\r\n```\r\n* Edit tests/TestMetacoin.sol\r\n```\r\nfunction testInitialBalanceUsingDeployedContract() public {\r\n    require(1==2);\r\n }\r\n```\r\n## Expected Behavior\r\n\r\n`truffle test` should fail.\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\n`truffle test` succeeds. Using `truffle develop` then `test` it fails.\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\nMac\r\nTruffle v4.0.5 (core: 4.0.5)\r\nSolidity v0.4.18 (solc-js)",
